---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | June Kato" description="Privacy policy for June Kato's freelance illustration website.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Review and customize this content before launch -->
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-md p-4 mb-8">
        <strong>Note:</strong> This is placeholder content. Please review and update this privacy policy to reflect your actual data practices before launching your site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">
        When you visit this website, we may collect certain information automatically, including your IP address, browser type, and pages visited. If you contact us through the contact form, we collect the information you provide, such as your name and email address.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">
        We use the information we collect to respond to your inquiries, improve our website, and communicate with you about potential projects or commissions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">
        We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">
        If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through the contact form on this website.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
        Last updated: [Insert Date]
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
